{% macro video() %}
	<bolt-card-replacement-media>
    {% set video %}
      <video-js
        data-account="1900410236"
        data-player="r1CAdLzTW"
        data-embed="default"
        data-video-id="3861325118001"
        data-media-title
        data-media-durration
        controls
        class="c-base-video"></video-js>
    {% endset %}

    {% include '@bolt-elements-ratio/ratio.twig' with {
      content: video,
      ratio: 'wide'
    } only %}
	</bolt-card-replacement-media>
{% endmacro %}

{% macro image() %}
	<bolt-card-replacement-media>
		<bolt-image src="/images/placeholders/16x9.jpg" alt="A Rock Climber"></bolt-image>
	</bolt-card-replacement-media>
{% endmacro %}

{% macro body() %}
	<bolt-card-replacement-body>
		<bolt-text eyebrow>This is an eyebrow</bolt-text>
		<bolt-text headline>This is a headline</bolt-text>
		<bolt-text>This is a paragraph.</bolt-text>
	</bolt-card-replacement-body>
{% endmacro %}

{% macro body_clickable() %}
	<bolt-card-replacement-body>This is a card-replacement with an overall link that makes the whole card-replacement clickable.</bolt-card-replacement-body>
{% endmacro %}

{% macro body_with_link() %}
	<bolt-card-replacement-body>This is a card-replacement with an overall link that makes the whole card-replacement clickable, while the body can still have <a target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="https://boltdesignsystem.com/docs" class="e-bolt-text-link">text links</a> that would go somewhere else.</bolt-card-replacement-body>
{% endmacro %}

{% macro actions() %}
	<bolt-card-replacement-actions>
		<bolt-card-replacement-action url="https://amazon.com">
			Internal link
		</bolt-card-replacement-action>
		<bolt-card-replacement-action url="https://yahoo.com" external>
			External link
		</bolt-card-replacement-action>
	</bolt-card-replacement-actions>
{% endmacro %}

{% import _self as card_replacement_demo %}


{% set card_replacement_web_component_demo %}
<bolt-card-replacement>
	{% include card_replacement_demo.image() %}
	{% include card_replacement_demo.body() %}
	{% include card_replacement_demo.actions() %}
</bolt-card-replacement>
{% endset %}

{% set simple_link_demo %}
<bolt-card-replacement url="https://google.com" url-text="Go to google.com">
	{% include card_replacement_demo.image() %}
	{% include card_replacement_demo.body_clickable() %}
</bolt-card-replacement>
{% endset %}

{% set advanced_link_demo %}
<bolt-card-replacement>
	<bolt-card-replacement-link custom-attribute="foo" html-attribute="bar">
		<a href="https://google.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Go to google.com</a>
	</bolt-card-replacement-link>
	{% include card_replacement_demo.image() %}
	{% include card_replacement_demo.body_clickable() %}
</bolt-card-replacement>
{% endset %}

{% set nested_links_demo %}
<bolt-card-replacement url="https://google.com">
	{% include card_replacement_demo.video() %}
	{% include card_replacement_demo.body_with_link() %}
	{% include card_replacement_demo.actions() %}
</bolt-card-replacement>
{% endset %}

<div class="e-bolt-wrapper">
	<bolt-text headline>
		Web Component Usage
	</bolt-text>
	<bolt-text>
		Bolt card-replacement is a web component, you can simply use
		<code>&lt;bolt-card-replacement&gt;</code>
		in the markup to make it render. Its inner content is comprised of
		<code>&lt;bolt-card-replacement-media&gt;</code>,
		<code>&lt;bolt-card-replacement-body&gt;</code>, and
		<code>&lt;bolt-card-replacement-actions&gt;</code>.
	</bolt-text>
	<div class="t-bolt-light u-bolt-margin-bottom-small u-bolt-padding-medium">
		{% include '@bolt-components-grid/grid.twig' with {
			items: [
				{
					column_start: '1',
					column_span: '12 6@small',
					content: card_replacement_web_component_demo,
				},
			]
		} only %}
	</div>
	<div class="u-bolt-margin-bottom-large">
		{% include '@bolt-components-code-snippet/code-snippet.twig' with {
      content: card_replacement_web_component_demo,
      lang: 'html',
      mode: 'dark',
    } only %}
	</div>

	<bolt-text headline>
		Simple Link Usage
	</bolt-text>
	<bolt-text>
		The simplest way to make the whole card-replacement clickable is by passing a link address to the
		<code>url</code>
		prop on the main
		<code>&lt;bolt-card-replacement&gt;</code>
		component itself. Also include the
		<code>url-text</code>
		prop for accessibility.
	</bolt-text>
	<div class="t-bolt-light u-bolt-margin-bottom-small u-bolt-padding-medium">
		{% include '@bolt-components-grid/grid.twig' with {
			items: [
				{
					column_start: '1',
					column_span: '12 6@small',
					content: simple_link_demo,
				},
			]
		} only %}
	</div>
	<div class="u-bolt-margin-bottom-large">
		{% include '@bolt-components-code-snippet/code-snippet.twig' with {
      content: simple_link_demo,
      lang: 'html',
      mode: 'dark',
    } only %}
	</div>

	<bolt-text headline>
		Advanced Link Usage
	</bolt-text>
	<bolt-text>
		Insert a
		<code>&lt;bolt-card-replacement-link&gt;</code>
		inside
		<code>&lt;bolt-card-replacement&gt;</code>
		and you can pass more than just
		<code>url</code>.
		<code>&lt;bolt-card-replacement-link&gt;</code>
		is similar to
		<code>&lt;bolt-link&gt;</code>. You can add custom attributes to
		<code>&lt;bolt-card-replacement-link&gt;</code>
		and insert a semantic
		<code>&lt;a&gt;</code>
		or
		<code>&lt;button&gt;</code>
		element inside.
	</bolt-text>
	<div class="t-bolt-light u-bolt-margin-bottom-small u-bolt-padding-medium">
		{% include '@bolt-components-grid/grid.twig' with {
			items: [
				{
					column_start: '1',
					column_span: '12 6@small',
					content: advanced_link_demo,
				},
			]
		} only %}
	</div>
	<div class="u-bolt-margin-bottom-large">
		{% include '@bolt-components-code-snippet/code-snippet.twig' with {
      content: advanced_link_demo,
      lang: 'html',
      mode: 'dark',
    } only %}
	</div>

	<bolt-text headline>
		Nested Links
	</bolt-text>
	<bolt-text>
		While making the whole card-replacement clickable, you are still able to insert nested links as needed. Any
		<code>&lt;bolt-link&gt;</code>,
		<code>&lt;bolt-card-replacement-link&gt;</code>, and
		<code>&lt;bolt-card-replacement-action&gt;</code>
		will work as expected.
	</bolt-text>
	<div class="t-bolt-light u-bolt-margin-bottom-small u-bolt-padding-medium">
		{% include '@bolt-components-grid/grid.twig' with {
			items: [
				{
					column_start: '1',
					column_span: '12 6@small',
					content: nested_links_demo,
				},
			]
		} only %}
	</div>
	<div class="u-bolt-margin-bottom-large">
		{% include '@bolt-components-code-snippet/code-snippet.twig' with {
      content: nested_links_demo,
      lang: 'html',
      mode: 'dark',
    } only %}
	</div>
</div>
